divs: sighting detailswe were awake with our baby at 4:45\5 am and looked out over the river in westport ma. we my husband and i, saw a bright light in the dark sky- there were no stars near it, no city lights and it was before sunrise.it looked as though orange, yellow, white colors were fading in and out of the light when we saw it. we looked at it through binoculars and it was bright and steady for a good 45 minutes before we finished feeding our son and going back to sleep- we woke up at 7 and the sun was up and it was gone-
